news.title: After 30-year wait, Prayagraj development body begins process to give land to allottees
news.para: Early this month, PDA has come up with this unique scheme, ‘Mission Sangam’, following which the authorities have identified 415 individuals who were allotted land by the PDA but they failed to get the possession for various reasons.

news.title: Casagrand plans for IPO in 2022
news.para: Casagrand plans to strengthen its presence in Bengaluru and will be investing Rs 1,250 crore in the next one year. The company is also looking to enter Hyderabad market with an initial investment of Rs 1,500 crore.

news.title: Construction sites in Noida flout rules, but no action yet: Residents
news.para: The residents alleged they hadn’t received any response from the Uttar Pradesh Pollution Control Board despite several tweets on the violations.
